<TEXT>
   ("Crocodile teeth are useless for chewing." -- News item)
                                                                                                       

   Oh, crocodile
   With teeth on view,
   Though those dentures
   Cannot chew,
   I'd just as soon
   Not swim with you.
   -- Robert Gordon.
